without us again.

157
00:17:11,397 --> 00:17:12,989
Sorry.

158
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:16,358
Sorry.

159
00:17:16,769 --> 00:17:19,237
You must tell me before you leave.

160
00:17:20,272 --> 00:17:23,730
I don't know how it was before, but
you cannot run around by yourselves.

161
00:17:23,942 --> 00:17:26,433
You have no idea
how dangerous it is here.

162
00:17:29,882 --> 00:17:32,043
Besides, it's dinnertime.

163
00:17:33,285 --> 00:17:34,616
Raymond, is the grill ready?

164
00:17:36,288 --> 00:17:37,550
Yeah.

165
00:17:37,756 --> 00:17:39,314
Thank you.

166
00:17:42,161 --> 00:17:43,253
Hungry?

167
00:17:49,401 --> 00:17:50,925
Come on.

168
00:18:30,609 --> 00:18:34,136
Yes, I'm checking now.
It's okay, Abby. Go back to bed.

169
00:18:48,193 --> 00:18:49,524
There's someone outside.

170
00:18:51,530 --> 00:18:54,055
Look, I called it in, Abby.
They're gonna make a drive-by.

171
00:18:54,266 --> 00:18:55,528
I just saw someone outside!

172
00:18:55,734 --> 00:18:58,965
I heard you, and it's
gonna be okay. All right?

173
00:18:59,872 --> 00:19:02,363
Abby, look, don't worry about it.

174
00:19:02,574 --> 00:19:04,041
Abby.

175
00:19:04,243 --> 00:19:05,938
Listen to me.

176
00:19:06,145 --> 00:19:10,206
- Abby!
- Ethan. Are you okay?

177
00:19:11,383 --> 00:19:13,408
He's scared.

178
00:19:15,454 --> 00:19:18,321
This is why we stay
close to the house, okay?

179
00:19:19,191 --> 00:19:21,716
Abby said she saw
someone outside.

180
00:19:22,361 --> 00:19:24,886
It's the middle of the night.
Where were you?

181
00:19:30,302 --> 00:19:31,997
Do you want to sleep
with Mommy tonight?

182
00:19:32,204 --> 00:19:34,365
It's fine. I'll stay with him.

183
00:19:36,074 --> 00:19:38,235
I want Abby.

184
00:19:43,448 --> 00:19:46,417
Okay. You're both safe now.

185
00:20:27,226 --> 00:20:28,420
Here, baby.

186
00:20:29,294 --> 00:20:31,353
There she is. Have a seat.

187
00:20:31,964 --> 00:20:34,057
How many pancakes do you want?

188
00:20:35,367 --> 00:20:37,460
- Two's fine.
- Okay.

189
00:20:37,669 --> 00:20:40,638
<i>- Raymond, breakfast.
- I'll be right down.</i>

190
00:20:43,942 --> 00:20:47,036
He is in his office
at 6 every morning.

191
00:20:47,246 --> 00:20:51,239
- I hope he doesn't wake you.
- Oh, no. I didn't hear him, it's fine.

192
00:20:51,450 --> 00:20:55,614
I need some help around
the house today. Can I get...

193
00:20:55,821 --> 00:20:57,413
...two volunteers?

194
00:21:07,399 --> 00:21:09,924
Ethan, you...
You'll help Eve with the laundry, okay?

195
00:21:10,135 --> 00:21:12,160
And I'll show you both how.

196
00:21:15,774 --> 00:21:17,674
All right. Look, Ethan.

197
00:21:17,876 --> 00:21:19,844
At the laundry. Okay.

198
00:21:20,045 --> 00:21:21,876
What you wanna
make sure is...

199
